<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="display-n">display <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'spleɪ/    美 /dɪ'spleɪ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>陈列；展览；表演：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a window display
橱窗陈列</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is always a huge public firework display on National Day.  
国庆节总会有大型的公开烟火表演。</p><footer>北师大① – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(特性、情感或能力的) 显示；表露：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He made a display of his learning. 
他卖弄了一下自己的学问。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-display">on display</h3>
<p>1.<strong>展出 (on show)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Jane paused in front of a counter where some attractive ties were on display.
简在一个柜台前停了下来，柜台上面展示着一些好看的领带。</p><footer>2009 广东</footer></div></div>